items.product_description:
Happy 30th Anniversary Air Max 90. The Air Max 90 (originally known as the Air Max III until the year 2000) is a timeless shoe. It has served as the perfect canvas for many different colorways over the years. The silhouette has been re-crafted time and time again, every remodel however has stayed true to the original. Product Details
Nike Air Max 90 “Royal”
Men's  low-top running lifestyle shoe
Mesh upper with nubuck overlay
Features mesh at toe box and collar lining
Nike Swoosh on sides
Rubber eyelets featured
Full Lace-up closure on front
Polyester textile tongue with Nike Air Max branding
Cushioned heel collar
Rubber heel tab with Nike Air branding
Air Max branding on sides
Foam midsole with MAX AIR bubble unit for support and lightweight comfort
Rubber outsole for traction
Colors: White/Royal/Black
Fit: True to SizeFabric: Synthetic Materials
